section.def:
court-related matter (法院相關事宜) means—(a)an act or matter that relates to a proceeding in the District Court;
                    or(b)a service, or other matter, made available or provided by the District
                    Court, the Registry or an office of the District Court;

e-fee (電子費用) means a fee
            that is payable under these Rules for a court-related matter that is carried out by
            means of an e-system;
